original_title: The Brian Setzer Orchestra: One Rockin' Night - Live In Montreal
overview: ONE ROCKIN' NIGHT: LIVE IN MONTREAL captures a live performance by the Brian Setzer Orchestra at the 1995 Montreal Jazz Festival. The 17-piece big band performs 16 classic songs including "Good Rockin' Daddy," "Sittin' On It," "Route 66," "Rock This Town," and " Stray Cat Strut."
title: The Brian Setzer Orchestra: One Rockin' Night - Live In Montreal
